OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FShowers or longer spells of
OL,6,Frain at first, perhaps locally heavy.
OL,7,FThen drier and brighter conditions
OL,8,Fspread east, although scattered
OL,9,Fafternoon showers could develop for a
OL,10,Ftime. Strong winds likely along the
OL,11,Fcoast this morning, then easing.
OL,12,FTemperatures near average.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FDry with clear periods and
OL,15,Ftemperatures quickly falling this
OL,16,Fevening. Overnight becoming cloudy
OL,17,Fwith isolated showers and also windy
OL,18,Falong the coast. Later rain reaches
OL,19,Fwestern areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
