OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FRain quickly continues east,
OL,6,Fthen eases to turn light and patchy by
OL,7,Flate morning, with most places
OL,8,Fbecoming dry and cloudy through the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Breezy inland, windy along
OL,10,Fthe coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,13,Fand breezy with bright or sunny spells
OL,14,FMonday. Tuesday and Wednesday
OL,15,Fpredominantly cloudy with a chance of
OL,16,Fpatchy light rain or drizzle at times.
OL,17,FGenerally mild or very mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
